
######################################
#  Adventuron                        #
######################################

loading_screen = loading_screen

start_at = nicobar_park

######################################
#  Variables                         #
######################################

integers {
   day_spend_walls_enigma : integer "0";
}

######################################
#  Locations                         #
######################################

locations {

   bookshop : location "You are at the book shop." ;

   church : location "You are in front of the church." ;

   church_tower : location "You are in the church's tower." ;

   coocoo_cafe : location "You are at the famous Coocoo Cafe, where there is always a variety of pigeons on the roof. Enter inside!" ;
   
   coocoo_inside : location "You are inside the Coocoo Cafe. There are no customers." ;

   montauk_beach : location "Montauk is the place where lovers like to meet." ;

   nicobar_park : location "You are in Nicobar Park." ;

   pigeon_fountain : location "You are in the Pigeon Fountain." ;

   pigeon_route : location "You are in the Life or Bread labyrinth game.\n\nMove once a day and get the bread before a week to survive or this tomb will be your tomb!" ;

   robin_room : location "You are in Robin's bedroom, checking that Larry's friend Columbia safely delivered Robin's present." ;

   santa_cellar : location "This is Santa's cellar, where you can find different potions to keep him cheerful and full of energy." ;

   south_park : location "You are in the South of Nicobar Park." ;

   walls_n: location "";
   walls_ns: location "";
   walls_nse: location "";
   walls_nsen: location "";
   walls_nsene: location "";
   walls_nsenee: location "";
   walls_nses: location "";
   walls_nsesn: location "";
   walls_nsesnn: location "";
   walls_nss: location "";
   walls_s: location "";
   walls_se: location "";
   walls_see: location "";
   walls_win: location "You arrived at the end! Congratulations!";
}

######################################
#  Connections                       #
######################################

connections {

   from, direction, to = [
   santa_cellar, southeast, nicobar_park,
   nicobar_park, north, montauk_beach,
   nicobar_park, west, coocoo_cafe,
   nicobar_park, south, south_park,
   coocoo_cafe, south, bookshop,
   coocoo_cafe, enter, coocoo_inside, 
   bookshop, east, south_park,
   nicobar_park, northeast, pigeon_fountain,
   south_park, south, church,
   church, south, church_tower,
   montauk_beach, north, robin_room,
   nicobar_park, east, pigeon_route,

   pigeon_route, north_oneway, walls_n,
   walls_n, south_oneway, walls_ns,
   walls_ns, east_oneway, walls_nse,
   walls_nse, north_oneway, walls_nsen,
   walls_nsen, east_oneway, walls_nsene,
   walls_nsene, east_oneway, walls_nsenee,
   walls_nse, south_oneway, walls_nses,
   walls_nses, north_oneway, walls_nsesn,
   walls_ns, south_oneway, walls_nss,
   walls_nss, east_oneway, walls_see,
   pigeon_route, south_oneway, walls_s,
   walls_s, east_oneway, walls_se,
   walls_se, east_oneway, walls_see,
   walls_see, north_oneway, walls_nse,
   walls_nsesn, east_oneway, walls_win,
   walls_nsesn, north_oneway, walls_nsesnn,
   walls_nsesnn, east_oneway, walls_nsenee,
   walls_nsenee, south_oneway, walls_win,
   ]

}

######################################
#  Objects                           #
######################################

objects {

grateful_waitress : scenery "The Coocoo Cafe team is grateful for your help. You got rid of all extra cookies and croissants...  But where?" ;

intro : scenery "yourself crying and knowing that all children will think they were bad this year and didn't deserve a present" at = "nicobar_park" ;

after_intro : scenery "the pigeons following Larry to distribute all the presents" ;

pigeon_book : object "a book \'Pigeons love bread\'" at = "nicobar_park" ;

larry : scenery "Larry, the leader of the pack of pigeons." at = "montauk_beach";

bin : scenery "a beautiful Art Deco bin." at = "coocoo_cafe";

bread : object "a generous loaf of bread";

flying_pigeon : scenery "a pigeon singing even though its beak is carrying a Sappy Meal bag: \' lovers meet in Montauk Beach, lalala \'" at = "nicobar_park";

new_pigeon : scenery "a pigeon singing even though its beak is carrying a dumbbell: \'Best carriers meet in Montauk Beach, lalala \'";

robin : scenery "Robin is happily screaming 'I can't wait to play Call Of Beauty!'" at = "robin_room" ;

helping_larry : scenery "Larry who will now motivate the whole pigeon troop to deliver all presents." ;

waitress : scenery "a waitress from Coocoo Cafe. She looks very tired." at = "coocoo_inside" ;

}

######################################
#  Barriers                          #
######################################

barriers {

   block_larry : block {

      location = robin_room
      message  = The path is blocked by Larry
      block_when_exists = larry

   }

}

######################################
#  On Startup                        #
######################################

on_startup {

   : print "Type VERB NOUN with the keyboard to advance in the game." ;
   : print "e.g. EXAMINE PIGEON to take a closer look at a PIGEON." ;
   : print "GET BREAD (or TAKE BREAD) to take BREAD and add it to your inventory." ;
   : press_any_key ;
   : print "To travel, type NORTH, EAST, SOUTH, WEST (or N, E, S, W)" ;
   : press_any_key ;
   : print "To check your inventory, type INVENTORY (or I, POCKETS)" ;
   : press_any_key ;
   : print "Christmas is coming tonight, everyone cannot wait to open presents. While you are organizing the distribution, all your reindeer suddenly become unable to move." ;
   : print "How will you find a way to send all presents in time for the big day?" ;
   : print "Press any key to continue." ;

   : press_any_key ;

}

######################################
#  On Describe                       #
######################################

on_describe {
   : if (is_present "larry") {
      : print "Larry says, \"I'm glad you met me in Montauk. I hope you've not come empty-handed.\"." ;
   }

   : if (is_at "robin_room" ) {
      : print "CONGRATULATIONS !" ;
      : print "YOU WON THE GAME !" ;
      : print "THANKS TO YOU, ROBIN AND ALL KIDS AROUND THE WORLD WILL BE HAPPY ON CHRISTMAS!" ;
      : play_music sound="music_victory";
      : press_any_key ;
      : clear_screen;
      : stop_music;
      : win_game ;
   }
   : if (is_at "pigeon_route" ) {
       : set_integer var = "day_spend_walls_enigma" value = "6";
   }
   : if (is_at "walls_s" ) {
       : add var = "day_spend_walls_enigma" value = "1" ;
   }
   : if (is_at "walls_nsen" ) {
       : add var = "day_spend_walls_enigma" value = "1" ;
   }
   : if (is_at "walls_nss" ) {
       : add var = "day_spend_walls_enigma" value = "2" ;
   }
   : if (is_at "walls_nsesnn" ) {
       : add var = "day_spend_walls_enigma" value = "2" ;
   }
   : if (is_at "walls_win" ) {
      : if (day_spend_walls_enigma == 6) {
            # should only show "Retry" phrase when object has not been won
            : print "You did it in the shortest time possible, you win fresh bread! \n\nRetry it taking the slowest path to get a consolation (=loser) prize.";
      }
      : else_if (day_spend_walls_enigma == 10) {
            # should only show "Retry" phrase when object has not been won
            : print "You did it in the longest time possible, you win stale bread!\n(and you kept your life YAY!)\n\nRetry it taking the least time possible whenever you want.";
      }
      : else {
            # should only show "Retry" phrase when object has not been won
            : print "You spent too much time and won NOTHING!\n(but you kept your life YAY!)\n\nRetry it taking even more time or taking the least possible time!";
      }
      : press_any_key ;
      : goto "nicobar_park";
      : redescribe;
   }
}

######################################
#  On Command                        #
######################################

on_command {

   : match "get bag; pick bag"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "Pigeons are too high, and you are not fit enough to get to the roof." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "The pigeon is very high in the sky, and you cannot fly without a reindeer." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine beach"  {
      : if (is_at "montauk_beach") {
         : print "The beach is quiet today." ;
      }
   }

   : match "check bin; examine bin"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "There is sometimes a loaf of bread inside the bin." ;
      }
   }

   : match "give bread"  {
      : if (is_present "larry" && is_carried "bread") {
         : print "Larry takes the loaf of bread and says. \"Alright, we'll help you distribute the presents. Let's go!\" ";
         : destroy "bread" ;
         : swap o1 = "larry"  o2 = "helping_larry" ;
         : swap o1 = "intro"  o2 = "after_intro" ;
         : swap o1 = "flying_pigeon"  o2 = "new_pigeon" ;
      }
   }

   : match "get bread; pick bread"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe" && has_not_created "bread" && is_exists "grateful_waitress") {
        : print "You take a big loaf of bread from the bin." ;
        : pocket "bread";
      }
   }

   : match "examine book; read book"  {
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "Inside it says \'Pigeons love carrying heavy objects, but need energy to do so.\'" ;
      }
   }

   : match "get book; pick book"  {
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park" && has_not_created "pigeon_book") {
        : print "You take the book" ;
        : pocket "pigeon_book";
      }
   }
   
   : match "clean cafe; tidy cafe"  {
      : if (is_present "waitress") {
         : print "You are helping the Coocoo Cafe team.";
         : swap o1 = "waitress"  o2 = "grateful_waitress" ;
         ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine cafe"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "The Coocoo Cafe is about to close, but there is so much left to do!" ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine children"  {
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "You are the only child here." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine coocoo"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "The Coocoo Cafe is about to close, but there is so much left to do!" ;
      }
   }
   
   : match "clean coocoo; tidy coocoo"  {
      : if (is_present "waitress") {
         : print "You are helping the Coocoo Cafe team.";
         : swap o1 = "waitress"  o2 = "grateful_waitress" ;
         ;
      }
   }

   : match "get larry; pick larry"  {
      : if (is_at "montauk_beach") {
         : print "Pigeons are not pocket monsters, you cannot just catch them." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine larry; talk larry"  {
      : if (is_present "larry") {
         : clear_screen;
         : print "\"Can't you see we are all hungry?\", says Larry." ;
         : press_any_key ;
         : redescribe;
      }
   }

   : match "examine lovers"  {
      : if (is_at "montauk_beach") {
         : print "You see pigeons making a heart shape in the sky." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "You are alone here." ;
      }
   }

   : match "get meal; pick meal"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "Pigeons are too high, and you are not fit enough to get to the roof." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "The pigeon is very high in the sky, and you cannot fly without a reindeer." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine montauk"  {
      : if (is_at "montauk_beach") {
         : print "The beach is quiet today." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine park"  {
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "You are alone, there is nothing to do here and it's raining." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine pigeon; examine pigeons"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "You see pigeons eating and flying with colorful doggy bags. It's like a very busy restaurant." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "montauk_beach") {
         : print "Pigeons are flying, exercising and eating. Very healthy." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "The pigeon looks happy and busy." ;
      }
   }

   : match "get pigeon; pick pigeon; talk pigeon"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "Pigeons are too high, and you are not fit enough to get to the roof." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "montauk_beach") {
         : print "Pigeons are not pocket monsters, you cannot just catch them." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "The pigeon is very high in the sky, and you cannot fly without a reindeer." ;
      }
      : if (is_present "larry") {
         : clear_screen;
         : print "\"Can't you see we are all hungry?\", says Larry." ;
         : press_any_key ;
         : redescribe;
      }
   }

   : match "examine present"  {
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "There are no presents here." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine roof"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "You see pigeons eating and flying with colorful doggy bags. It's like a very busy restaurant." ;
      }
   }
   
   : match "help waitress"  {
      : if (is_present "waitress") {
         : print "You are helping the Coocoo Cafe team.";
         : swap o1 = "waitress"  o2 = "grateful_waitress" ;
         ;
      }
   }

   : match "look yourself; talk yourself"  {
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "You are alone, there is nothing to do here and it's raining." ;
      }
   }

}

assets {
   sounds {
      music_victory : sound_sample "https://ea.gizal.org/okfeather/coocoo_cafe.mp3" ;
   }
   graphics {
      coocoo_cafe    : base64_png "";
      loading_screen : base64_png "";
      montauk_beach  : base64_png "";
      nicobar_park   : base64_png "";
      robin_room     : base64_png "";
walls_nsesn : base64_png "";
walls_nsesnn : base64_png "";
walls_n : base64_png "";
walls_ns : base64_png "";

walls_nsen : base64_png "";

pigeon_route : base64_png "";
   }
}
